ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: the course is well designed so you take away a strong foundation in networks, even if the technology changes you now know how to think about the problem and how people come up with solutions etc
If you are interested in learning about the Internet, how it works and the technologies that make it possible take this course.
I have already recommended the course to other students.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: excellent foundational knowledge of networks that i can take with me
Essential course for system-oriented CS studentsGave me appropriate background for my research in distributed systems
This course helps me to better understand the networks and system topics.
